This repository builds on and credits the following third-party projects.

- `quest/` and `benchmark/` are built on top of `facebookresearch/co-tracker`
  (https://github.com/facebookresearch/co-tracker), licensed CC BY-NC 4.0.
  Base CoTracker3 modules these files depend on (cotracker3_offline.py,
  model_utils.py, blocks.py, embeddings.py, the base cotracker.py) are
  upstream code and are not included in this repo; see `quest/README.md`.

- `interactive_repair/nninteractive_corrector.py` integrates with
  `MIC-DKFZ/nnInteractive` (https://github.com/MIC-DKFZ/nnInteractive),
  licensed CC BY-NC-SA 4.0. nnInteractive itself and its trained weights
  are not vendored in this repo; obtain them separately under their license.

- `dataset_prep/` generates synthetic data from PartNet-Mobility
  (Mo et al., CVPR 2019) rendered in SAPIEN (Xiang et al., CVPR 2020).
  Neither the PartNet-Mobility mesh/URDF assets nor SAPIEN itself are
  redistributed here; obtain PartNet-Mobility under its own license.

- Evaluation baselines referenced in `downstream_causal/` (CoTracker2/3,
  AllTracker, DenseTrack2D, BootsTAPIR, TAPIR, V-JEPA2, DINOv2) are used via
  their official pretrained checkpoints, not redistributed in this repo.
